## Additional Terms for ShopifyScope Intelligence Platform

This software is designed for legitimate business intelligence and market research
purposes. Users are responsible for:

1. Respecting website terms of service and robots.txt files
2. Implementing appropriate rate limiting to avoid overwhelming target servers
3. Using the intelligence gathered in compliance with applicable data protection laws
4. Not using this software for any malicious or harmful purposes

The ShopifyScope Intelligence Platform is intended to help businesses make
data-driven decisions through ethical and responsible e-commerce analytics.
